香港商IT solution公司誠徵 C#.NET 工程師+SA
正職, 無須駐點

【.Net Engineer 】三年以上經驗

• Over 3 years of experience on HTML programming, include JavaScript, jQuery and HTML5
• Over 3 years of experience on ASP.NET MVC programming
• 1 year of experience on MS SQL Server
• Experience in cloud, e.g. Azure, AWS, etc. is an advantage
• Fluent in English

【Sr. SA 】需英文精通/可配合短期出差
Duties:
• Report to Project Manager or General Manager (for Architect role);
• Collect, understand and document requirements from users;
• Design solution according to the requirements;
• Produce system blueprint;
• Plan and lead the activities on system development life cycle;
• Work with test team to assure software quality;
• Conduct Proof of Concept (PoC) on solutions;
• Lead and direct programmers on system development; and
• Plan and lead system deployment;
Requirements:
• Good skills and experienced conducting user requirement elicitation activities, e.g. interview, workshop, questionnaire, etc.;
• Good analytic skills to abstract critical information from requirements, business process documents, etc.;
• Good communication and presentation skills to communicate system design to key stakeholders;
• Good understanding and experience in modern application architecture, e.g. SOA, Micro-services, etc.
• Good knowledge on programming design patterns
• Good knowledge on development approaches, e.g. Test-Driven Development, Behaviour-Driven Development, Scrum, etc.
• Knowledge and experience on Application Lifecycle Management or DevOps tools will be an advantage;
• At least 5 years of experience on ASP.NET development with C#;
• Good knowledge and experience on HTML programming, include JQuery, JSON, Javascript, etc.; and
• Experience on MS Azure or AWS will be an advantage.



